{"changelogUrl":"https://ghost.org/changelog/","posts":[{"title":"Audience feedback","feature_image":"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/audience-feedback-final-1.png","custom_excerpt":null,"html":"\u003cp\u003eThe new audience feedback feature gives your readers the opportunity to react to your content directly at the bottom of a newsletter.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/Email-Screenshot.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1670\" height=\"1566\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Email-Screenshot.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Email-Screenshot.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Email-Screenshot.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/Email-Screenshot.png 1670w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eNow you can establish a direct connection with your audience when it matters most — and gain a better understanding of the types of content that are resonating with your audience (and those that aren't).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-container\"\u003e\u003cvideo src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/media/2022/10/How-Audience-Feedback-Settings-Work.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/2550x1820/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"2550\" height=\"1820\" loop autoplay muted playsinline preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/Settings-Email-newsletter-Publisher-Weekly.png') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\" /\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-overlay\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-large-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player-container kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-pause-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003crect x=\"3\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003crect x=\"14\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-current-time\"\u003e0:00\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-time\"\u003e/\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-duration\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-seek-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-playback-rate\"\u003e1\u0026#215;\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-unmute-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAudience feedback can be enabled in the newsletter settings, and the reactions of your audience can be found in the post analytics for each individual newsletter.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/Post-Analytics-More-Like-This.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1258\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/Post-Analytics-More-Like-This.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/Post-Analytics-More-Like-This.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/Post-Analytics-More-Like-This.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/Post-Analytics-More-Like-This.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/pricing/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGhost(Pro)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e users can log in and start enjoying audience feedback right away! If you're a developer, self-hosting Ghost, you'll need to \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003eupd\u003c/a\u003eate\u003c/a\u003e to the latest version to get access to everything that's new.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","slug":"audience-feedback","url":"https://ghost.org/changelog/audience-feedback/","published_at":"2022-11-02T16:29:38.000+00:00"},{"title":"Member growth sources","feature_image":"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/member-attribution-final.png","custom_excerpt":null,"html":"\u003cp\u003eAnalytics in Ghost just got a major update, giving you the tools you need to understand how your audience is growing!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe new member growth features allow you to understand the most popular referral sources where people discover your work, as well as which post or page people were reading at the time they decided to signup.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet's take a look at the new analytics you can find in Ghost Admin, starting today.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"top-sources\"\u003eTop sources\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eOn the dashboard, you can now see the top sources driving audience growth from around the web. These stats are filterable by 7, 30, and 90 days, and show top sources for both free and paid signups.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/top-sources-widget.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1966\" height=\"744\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/top-sources-widget.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/top-sources-widget.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/top-sources-widget.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/top-sources-widget.png 1966w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis gives you an overview of how many of your member signups are being driven from social media, referrals from other websites, from your SEO efforts, or any other type of external source. Read more about \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/help/custom-source/\"\u003ehow to create a custom source\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"post-analytics\"\u003ePost analytics\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eOver on your post analytics, you can now see the number of free signups and paid conversions generated by that specific post, along with the referral sources where those members came from — giving you a deeper understanding of how successful each piece of content is, and how people are finding your work.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/post-analytics.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1587\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/post-analytics.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/post-analytics.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/post-analytics.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/post-analytics.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you want to see exactly which members signed up from a specific post, you can also use a filter on the members list.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/filtering-members-source-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"770\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/filtering-members-source-1.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/filtering-members-source-1.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/filtering-members-source-1.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/filtering-members-source-1.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"individual-member-stats\"\u003eIndividual member stats\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor every new free member signup, and every new paid subscription, Ghost now shows you where on the web that person came from as well as what post or page they were on when they converted, right on the member profile page.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/member-profile-signup-info-highlighted-border.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1533\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/10/member-profile-signup-info-highlighted-border.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/10/member-profile-signup-info-highlighted-border.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/10/member-profile-signup-info-highlighted-border.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/10/member-profile-signup-info-highlighted-border.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003eA major benefit of having memberships on a content website is turning anonymous visitors into logged-in members, which in turn means you get access to \u003cem\u003ereliable\u003c/em\u003e data about where your audience comes from, and what content converts the most people.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis provides new ways to understand your business: \u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eBeing able to see which of your marketing efforts are paying off through growth sources allows you to decide where to focus your efforts. \u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eKnowing which content is converting the most provides valuable insights about what content to produce next.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThere's no need to install any integrations, or setup goals for member signups. In Ghost, member growth sources are tracked automatically, and presented to you exactly where you need it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/pricing/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGhost(Pro)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e users can log in and start enjoying member growth sources right away! If you're a developer, self-hosting Ghost, you'll need to \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003eupdate\u003c/a\u003e to the latest version to get access to everything that's new.\u003c/p\u003e","slug":"member-growth","url":"https://ghost.org/changelog/member-growth/","published_at":"2022-10-31T17:17:10.000+00:00"},{"title":"Update links in email newsletters","feature_image":"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/icon-center-almost-final.png","custom_excerpt":null,"html":"\u003cp\u003eHave you ever delivered an email newsletter only to find you included a broken link? Whether it was a typo, or a link to a tweet that has since been deleted, it happens — we've all been there.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWouldn't it be nice if you could fix links in email newsletters in the same way you can on a published post?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWell, now you can. The latest updates in Ghost make it possible to edit any link in a newsletter, even after it has been delivered to your audience. Now you never have to worry about broken links in emails again.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-container\"\u003e\u003cvideo src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/media/2022/10/edit-link-in-email.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/2250x1756/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"2250\" height=\"1756\" playsinline preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/media-thumbnail-ember353.jpg') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\" /\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-overlay\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-large-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player-container\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-pause-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003crect x=\"3\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003crect x=\"14\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-current-time\"\u003e0:00\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-time\"\u003e/\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-duration\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-seek-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-playback-rate\"\u003e1\u0026#215;\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-unmute-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAll you need to do is click into the post analytics, find the link that needs to be updated, and click to edit 🔮\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/pricing/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGhost(Pro)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e users can log in and start enjoying all of this right away! If you're a developer, self-hosting Ghost, you'll need to \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003eupdate\u003c/a\u003e to the latest version to get access to everything that's new.\u003c/p\u003e","slug":"update-links","url":"https://ghost.org/changelog/update-links/","published_at":"2022-10-24T17:01:59.000+00:00"},{"title":"Newsletter click analytics","feature_image":"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/email-clicks-fi-2.png","custom_excerpt":null,"html":"\u003cp\u003eBy popular demand, we just shipped email newsletter click analytics, which means every post sent as a newsletter shows both opens and clicks, directly on your post list. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/09/Post-List-Screenshot.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1370\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/Post-List-Screenshot.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/Post-List-Screenshot.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/Post-List-Screenshot.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/09/Post-List-Screenshot.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can also dig deeper into which links are being clicked, and how many times, by viewing the post analytics page for each newsletter. This shows the total number of unique members that clicked on any link, plus a full breakdown of how many members clicked each individual link in your newsletter ✨\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-wide\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/09/Post-Analytics-Screenshot-1.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1860\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/Post-Analytics-Screenshot-1.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/Post-Analytics-Screenshot-1.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/Post-Analytics-Screenshot-1.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w2400/2022/09/Post-Analytics-Screenshot-1.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 1200px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWant to drill down even further? No problem. Click any metric in the engagement section to get a full breakdown of exactly which members opened or clicked your newsletter.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-video-card kg-width-wide\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-container\"\u003e\u003cvideo src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/media/2022/10/email-clicks-5.mp4\" poster=\"https://img.spacergif.org/v1/1680x1080/0a/spacer.png\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1080\" loop autoplay muted playsinline preload=\"metadata\" style=\"background: transparent url('https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/media-thumbnail-ember68.jpg') 50% 50% / cover no-repeat;\" /\u003e\u003c/video\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-overlay\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-large-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player-container kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-player\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-play-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M23.14 10.608 2.253.164A1.559 1.559 0 0 0 0 1.557v20.887a1.558 1.558 0 0 0 2.253 1.392L23.14 13.393a1.557 1.557 0 0 0 0-2.785Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-pause-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003crect x=\"3\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003crect x=\"14\" y=\"1\" width=\"7\" height=\"22\" rx=\"1.5\" ry=\"1.5\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-current-time\"\u003e0:00\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"kg-video-time\"\u003e/\u003cspan class=\"kg-video-duration\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-seek-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\"\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-playback-rate\"\u003e1\u0026#215;\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-unmute-icon\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M15.189 2.021a9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h1.794a.249.249 0 0 1 .221.133 9.73 9.73 0 0 0 7.924 4.85h.06a1 1 0 0 0 1-1V3.02a1 1 0 0 0-1.06-.998Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"kg-video-mute-icon kg-video-hide\"\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.177 4.3a.248.248 0 0 0 .073-.176v-1.1a1 1 0 0 0-1.061-1 9.728 9.728 0 0 0-7.924 4.85.249.249 0 0 1-.221.133H5.25a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v2a3 3 0 0 0 3 3h.114a.251.251 0 0 0 .177-.073ZM23.707 1.706A1 1 0 0 0 22.293.292l-22 22a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.009.009a1 1 0 0 0 1.405-.009l6.63-6.631A.251.251 0 0 1 8.515 17a.245.245 0 0 1 .177.075 10.081 10.081 0 0 0 6.5 2.92 1 1 0 0 0 1.061-1V9.266a.247.247 0 0 1 .073-.176Z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003cinput type=\"range\" class=\"kg-video-volume-slider\" max=\"100\" value=\"100\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eEmail click analytics is enabled by default, and can be optionally disabled in the settings in Ghost Admin. Read more about \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/help/post-analytics/\"\u003enewsletter click analytics\u003c/a\u003e in Ghost.\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/pricing/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGhost(Pro)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e users can log in and start enjoying email click analytics right away! If you're a developer, self-hosting Ghost, you'll need to \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003eupdate\u003c/a\u003e to the latest version to access everything that's new.\u003c/p\u003e","slug":"newsletter-clicks","url":"https://ghost.org/changelog/newsletter-clicks/","published_at":"2022-10-03T16:12:06.000+00:00"},{"title":"History log","feature_image":"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/10/history-screenshot.png","custom_excerpt":null,"html":"\u003cp\u003eThe new history log in Ghost Admin allows you to see all staff user events that take place on your site in one place. Perfect for staying in the loop about when data is added, updated or changed by your team. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eStarting today, you can see changes made to posts, pages, tags, integrations, tiers, offers, settings, and staff member profiles, with more coming soon!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/09/history-screenshot.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1546\" srcset=\"https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w600/2022/09/history-screenshot.png 600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1000/2022/09/history-screenshot.png 1000w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/size/w1600/2022/09/history-screenshot.png 1600w, https://ghost.org/changelog/content/images/2022/09/history-screenshot.png 2360w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/pricing/\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGhost(Pro)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e users can log in and check out their History logs right away! If you're a developer, self-hosting Ghost, you'll need to \u003ca href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/update/\"\u003eupdate\u003c/a\u003e to the latest version to get access to everything that's new.\u003c/p\u003e","slug":"history-log","url":"https://ghost.org/changelog/history-log/","published_at":"2022-09-20T14:51:48.000+00:00"}]}